MILESTONE MEDIA is 30 years old! The trail-blazing company that brought us Static Shock has a brand new documentary on HBOMax detailing their meteoric rise and cultural impact as the most successful black-owned comic book company of all time! Join us as we discuss their rise, fall, and rise again in celebration of all things MILESTONE! Plus, we cover the Guardians of the Galaxy Vol 3 and The Flash trailers that were shown at the Super Bowl!  
  
If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
